                            "https://player.vimeo.com/video/63502573",
                            '<p>A fascinating story focusing on the emergence of a new world wide currency - now being accepted in Australia and elsewhere around the globe.  This is a snapshot of a time in history that could be very significant in the future.</p>'
                        ],
                        [ 
                            "What is Bitcoin", 
                            "https://player.vimeo.com/video/225926695",
                            '<p><strong>Client: Wondros</strong><br /><br />A short commissioned by Wondros in 2015, explaining the history and application of Bitcoin.</p></p>'
                        ],
                    ]
                    %>
                  
                    <!-- Start: Section Header -->
                    <div class="section-header text-left">
                        <h2 class="section-heading">Latest Videos</h2>
                        <!--<hr class="lines">-->
                    </div> <!-- End: Section Header -->
    
                    <div class="carousel-container margin-b-50 features-content">
                        <div class="carousel-wrapper owl-carousel padding-b-15 background-1 shadow">
                          
                            <% count = 1
                            videos.each do |video| 
                            if count <= 3 %>
                            <div class="item">
                                <div class="item-inner text-left">
                                    
                                    <!--  Start: Video Area  "PASTE YOUR VIDEO LINK HERE " -->
